eOptin,is,an,end,to,end,platform,that,authorizes,secure,connections,between,the,cloud,and,any,kind,of,electronic,device,or,appliance,It,also,enables,users,to,manage,those,connections,securely,from,anywhere,in,the,world,Users,can,connect,with,eOptin,s,authorization,services,from,within,their,own,application,or,device,via,the,eOptin,Authorize,Connect,API